* maximal in its column
<br>' minimal in its row
<br>There are 3 saddle ponts: the second row, columns 3, 6, and 7.
<br>The value of game is 6.
<br>The optimal strategy for the row player: choose the second row.
<br>The optimal strategy for the column player: use any mixture of columns
3,6,7.
