The last column goes by domination. What is left is a familiar&nbsp; symmetric
game.
<br>An optimal strategy for the row player is&nbsp;&nbsp; [1/3,1/3,1/3]<sup>T</sup>.
<br>An optimal strategy for the column player is [1/3,1/3,1/3,0].
<br>The value of game is 0.
